33280394.review:
Best roguelike I've played in a long while.

Pros:
Challenging gameplay that rewards knowledge above all;
Interesting classes and skill progression, even if some skills are lackluster compared to others;
Different challenge-routes which makes the risk/reward much higher;
Lovely pixel art and atmosphere;
Tight and responsive controls;

Cons:
Karma is real and it WILL kill you;
Achieving optimal equipment is a faraway dream, seeing as everything is RNG and enchanting scrolls are as rare as they come;
Rainbow Slime 2 stronk;
Not-amazing lategame progression;
Needs more lore;


Buy it for your friends and watch them ruin the entire run by being stupid.

